00:06:12.177 --> 00:06:13.908
download it there for free.

00:06:13.908 --> 00:06:16.922
Let's move on to step number
five, the Facebook Pixel.

00:06:16.922 --> 00:06:19.052
I don't want to be overly dramatic,

00:06:19.052 --> 00:06:22.945
but installing the Facebook
Pixel is absolutely essential.

00:06:22.945 --> 00:06:24.545
You need to use the
Facebook Pixel to track

00:06:24.545 --> 00:06:27.274
the actions that people
take on your website.

00:06:27.274 --> 00:06:29.164
Otherwise, you won't be able to determine

00:06:29.164 --> 00:06:31.625
how well your Facebook ad
campaigns are performing.

00:06:31.625 --> 00:06:33.006
And if you don't know
how they're performing,

00:06:33.006 --> 00:06:35.938
then you can't optimise
or make vital adjustments.

00:06:35.938 --> 00:06:37.870
Or even know if they are working!

00:06:37.870 --> 00:06:39.288
You also need to have the Facebook Pixel

00:06:39.288 --> 00:06:41.088
installed on your website to add people

00:06:41.088 --> 00:06:43.269
to your website custom audiences.

00:06:43.269 --> 00:06:45.528
Which you now know is the most powerful

00:06:45.528 --> 00:06:47.697
targeting option you can use in Facebook.

00:06:47.697 --> 00:06:49.837
Most website builders
now make it very easy

00:06:49.837 --> 00:06:51.594
for you to install the Facebook Pixel

00:06:51.594 --> 00:06:53.646
with specific places to put it.

00:06:53.646 --> 00:06:54.936
And if you have a WordPress website,

00:06:54.936 --> 00:06:56.968
you can use a simple plug-in to install it.

00:06:56.968 --> 00:06:58.378
However, if you're not technical

00:06:58.378 --> 00:06:59.677
and you can't work it out,

00:06:59.677 --> 00:07:01.477
it's worth paying a few bucks

00:07:01.477 --> 00:07:03.549
to get someone to install it for you.

00:07:03.549 --> 00:07:05.520
You can really easily
find someone to install

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:08.829
it for you on upwork.com and
it won't cost much at all.

00:07:08.829 --> 00:07:10.407
And when it comes to the Facebook Pixel,

00:07:10.407 --> 00:07:13.908
a pro tip is to use the
free Google Chrome extension

00:07:13.908 --> 00:07:16.547
called the Facebook Pixel Helper.

00:07:16.547 --> 00:07:18.290
It will show you if the Facebook Pixel is

00:07:18.290 --> 00:07:20.480
installed correctly on any page without

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:21.701
having to look at any code.

00:07:21.701 --> 00:07:24.781
Let's move onto step number
six, which is experimentation.

00:07:24.781 --> 00:07:27.989
It can be done, but it's
very rare to hit a home run

00:07:27.989 --> 00:07:29.240
on your first attempt.

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:31.712
When we create Facebook ad
campaigns for our clients,

00:07:31.712 --> 00:07:34.682
we create multiple variations
of just about everything.

00:07:34.682 --> 00:07:37.332
We test different ad
copy, different images,

00:07:37.332 --> 00:07:39.761
and of course, different
targeting options.

00:07:39.761 --> 00:07:41.792
It's crucial that you start advertising on

00:07:41.792 --> 00:07:43.202
Facebook with this in mind.

00:07:43.202 --> 00:07:45.482
I've seen too many people
create a single ad,

00:07:45.482 --> 00:07:47.721
advertise it to a single audience,

00:07:47.721 --> 00:07:49.042
have it not work very well,

00:07:49.042 --> 00:07:51.992
and then declare that Facebook
advertising doesn't work.

00:07:51.992 --> 00:07:53.992
That's crazy, and with the right attitude

00:07:53.992 --> 00:07:55.682
you can make sure that you don't fall

00:07:55.682 --> 00:07:57.224
victim to that mentality.

00:07:57.224 --> 00:07:59.224
Fortunately, it's really
easy to experiment

00:07:59.224 --> 00:08:00.762
with Facebook ad campaigns.

00:08:00.762 --> 00:08:03.551
Because Facebook recently
released a built-in

00:08:03.551 --> 00:08:04.973
split testing tool.

00:08:04.973 --> 00:08:06.861
At the moment you need a
business manager account

00:08:06.861 --> 00:08:08.100
to use the split testing tool.

00:08:08.100 --> 00:08:10.453
But it's well worth taking
the time to set that up,

00:08:10.453 --> 00:08:13.501
because this built in
split testing is fantastic.

00:08:13.501 --> 00:08:16.103
Now, I've saved the most
important step until last,

00:08:16.103 --> 00:08:17.714
and that is sales funnels.

00:08:17.714 --> 00:08:20.133
In step one, I talked
about how effective it is

00:08:20.133 --> 00:08:22.598
to target people that already know you.

00:08:22.598 --> 00:08:24.354
Well, the truth is, the more touch points

00:08:24.354 --> 00:08:26.404
your target market has with your company,

00:08:26.404 --> 00:08:29.032
and the more they get to
know you and your brand,

00:08:29.032 --> 00:08:32.314
the easier it is to sell
your products and services.

00:08:32.314 --> 00:08:34.423
We've worked with clients
with such a great following,

00:08:34.423 --> 00:08:35.874
that selling their products

00:08:35.874 --> 00:08:37.794
with Facebook ads is really easy.

00:08:37.794 --> 00:08:40.394
So how do you get people to
know your company quickly

00:08:40.394 --> 00:08:42.754
and ad them to your custom audiences?

00:08:42.754 --> 00:08:45.085
Well you can throw tonnes
of content up online

00:08:45.085 --> 00:08:46.914
and just hope people see it,

00:08:46.914 --> 00:08:49.484
or you can create a sales
funnel that takes people

00:08:49.484 --> 00:08:52.365
from cold prospects all
the way to repeat customers

00:08:52.365 --> 00:08:53.805
as fast as possible.

00:08:53.805 --> 00:08:56.487
By far the best way to
advertise to cold audiences

00:08:56.487 --> 00:08:58.927
on Facebook is to use a sales funnel.

00:08:58.927 --> 00:08:59.850
And to help you create a

00:08:59.850 --> 00:09:01.491
highly effective online sales funnels,

